				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					[["What kind of machines do cities have? Are they like the big one we saw in the village?"]],
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"「哎，城市里的机器是什么样的？　像我们之前看到的那种大家伙吗？」",
